data.description: This three bedroom, one bath, Millcreek cape cod will not disappoint! You'll love this fresh, well maintained home with tons of updates including fixtures, flooring and central AC. The kitchen boasts newer SS appliances, breakfast/wine bar and an open floor plan to for all of your holiday gatherings! Theres a newer front deck, fenced-in backyard and detached garage, all on a quiet street that's close to shopping, Presque Isle and more! Nothing left to do but move right in.
